yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.22,0:27:06.79,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,10,,{\i1}Te daré un\Nromance,{\i0}\N{\i1}te daré un\Nromance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.79,0:27:11.30,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Honto no yuki misete kuretara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.79,0:27:11.30,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si me muestras tu verdadero valor{\i0}
