Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.67,0:27:27.31,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Tokimeku mune ni{\i0}\N{\i1}kira-kira
hikatta yume o ageru yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.67,0:27:27.31,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Le daré a tu corazón\Nlatiente{\i0}\N{\i1}un sueño brillante y\Nresplandeciente.{\i0}